Partcipation is FREE just like last year. Photos from the Saamoohika Satya Narayana vratam conducted in March 2009 can be viewed at:
 
http://picasaweb.google.com/padmaja.bandaru/BostonSaamoohikaSatyanarayanaVratam
 
